Name: Chiptune Champion
About the game: Transform your keyboard into an instrument and play along to the melody of catchy chiptunes in this challenging rhythm game. Two game modes - strum and tap Three difficulty levels from rookie to expert Weekly and all-time leaderboards 40 official songs to choose from Track your own custom songs Share them with the community via the steam workshop Earn steam achievements Customise your keys
